overview: A struggling American writer and a fellow American expatriate begin a sordid affair among the chaos and discord of 1940 Paris, France on the brink of World War II.
tagline: In 1939, Elena went to Paris searching for her voice as a writer. What she found was her voice as a woman.
cast: Audie England|Costas Mandylor|Bernard Zette|Eric da Silva|Rory Campbell
